snippet.title: Team Rainbow Cinematic MIA Trailer | Rainbow Six Extraction
snippet.description:
Risk it all to save your fallen Operator!
On 20th January, Team Rainbow takes on the greatest threat they have ever known. 

Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six Extraction will be available on 20th January 2022 on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X | S, Xbox One, Stadia and PC.
For more info: 

www.rainbowsixextraction.com
